# Firebase Admin SDK (Service Account)
# 1. Go to Firebase Console → Project Settings → Service accounts
# 2. Click "Generate new private key"
# 3. Save the JSON file
# 4. Paste the ENTIRE JSON content as the value (not a file path!)
# Example: FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY={"type":"service_account","project_id":"...",...}
FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY=your-json-service-account-key-here

# Resend API Key (Optional, for email features)
# Get from https://resend.com/api-keys
